        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>United States-Mexico Tourism Improvement Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of State to develop and report to Congress a strategy to improve bilateral tourism between the United States and Mexico and third-party tourism to the two countries. The strategy shall involve dialogue and cooperation between the two governments, and it shall prioritize sectors including hospitality, retail, and cultural education. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
